name: Allah
meaning: Simbolically, 'A' stands for Allah, signifying the Original Man, the Asiatic Black Man, the Maker, the Owner, the Cream of the Planet Earth, Father of Civilization, and God of the Universe.

name: Be / Born
meaning: To exist. Born is to be brought into existence, which is mental or physical birth.

name: Cee
meaning: To see is to visualize and understand. To Cee is to have insight.

name: Divine
meaning: Nature that is pure and holy. Can not be mixed, diluted, or tampered with.

name: Equality
meaning: To be equal in all things. Knowledge, Wisdom, and Understanding.

name: Father
meaning: One who fathers the mental and physical. The foundation of the family.

name: God
meaning: The Supreme Being. The Blackman who has knowledge of himself.

name: He / Her
meaning: Those who have the power to build or destroy based on their level of intelligence.

name: Islam
meaning: I Self Lord And Master. Peace. The culture of the original man.

name: Justice
meaning: The reward or penalty for one's ways and actions.

name: King / Kingdom
meaning: One who leads and guides. Kingdom is the domain of the King.

name: Love / Hell / Right
meaning: Love is the highest elevation of understanding. Hell is a state of mind (low). Right is the proper way.

name: Master
meaning: One who knows and understands all things within his circumference.

name: Now / Nation / End
meaning: Now is the time. Nation is a group of civilized people. End is the conclusion.

name: Cipher
meaning: A circle consisting of 360 degrees. Completion.

name: Power
meaning: Truth. The light. The magnetic force.

name: Queen
meaning: The female counterpart of the King. She reflects the knowledge of God.

name: Rule / Ruler
meaning: To guide and lead in the right direction.

name: Self / Savior
meaning: One's own being. Savior is one who saves others by teaching the truth.

name: Truth / Square
meaning: That which is actual and factual. Square is truth (4 corners).

name: You / Universe
meaning: You are the universe. The sun, moon, and stars.

name: Victory
meaning: To overcome. To win.

name: Wisdom
meaning: To speak wise words and act wisely.

name: Unknown
meaning: That which is not known. Also represents equality (4 ways).

name: Why
meaning: The question most asked by the 85%. Seeking cause and effect.

name: Zig-Zag-Zig
meaning: Knowledge, Wisdom, Understanding. The path from A to Z.
